jd_content=Role: Marketing Manager

Location: Chennai | Experience: 5-10 years

About Us:
Join Ideas2it Technology, a fast-growing company driving innovative marketing strategies to grow our brand and impact.

Role Overview:
We're looking for a dynamic Marketing Manager to lead campaigns, drive engagement, and boost brand visibility across digital and offline channels.

What You'll Do:

1) Plan and execute marketing campaigns across social media, email, and other channels.
2) Analyze market trends and customer insights to optimize performance.
3) Collaborate with sales and product teams to align marketing initiatives.
4) Track KPIs, ROI, and campaign effectiveness.
5) Manage marketing budgets and ensure brand consistency.

What We're Looking For:

i) Bachelor's degree in Marketing, Business, or related field.
ii) 5-10 years of marketing experience, preferably in digital and offline channels.
iii) Strong communication, leadership, and project management skills.
iv) Creative, analytical, and results-driven mindset.

Why Join Us:

i) Competitive salary & performance incentives
ii) Career growth opportunities
iii) Collaborative, innovative work environment
